Description:
Ballistics of the 130x845 3VOF11 fired from the M-46 gun, with the 3OF3 proejctile and full variable charge 54-Zh-482. In the PRC the ammunition and gun is copied with modification as the WB005P high-explosive fragmentation shell, fired from the Type 1959 130mm gun. The Type 1959 is improved with the Type 1959-1 variant, the design finalized in 1970.

Peak breech pressure of 3150 kgf/cm^2 copper crusher, converts to 345.7 MPa piezoelectric at a factor of 1.12 x 0.098. Chamber length is 991mm when new. The full variable charge loads DG-3 (双芳-3) 23/1 or NDT-3 23/1 grains, and supports two velocity zones, as follows:

Zone  Charge Muzzle Velocity
      kg     m/s
full  12.9   930
No.1  11.0   810

Reference table in ФИЗИЧЕСКИЕ ОСНОВЫ: устройства и функционирования стрелково-пушечного, артиллерийского и ракетного оружия, cross referencing chapter 1959年130毫米加农炮 in 《国产火炮手册 说明部分》
